121
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:35,450
I'll bluff Qing Dai.

122
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:38,800
Hong Guo has already confessed.

123
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:40,159
You pretended to be the Green Ghost Bandits

124
00:07:40,159 --> 00:07:42,159
