125
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,040
Pretend?

126
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,680
Green Ghost Bandits?

127
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:56,080
I suppose Lord Mo suspects me because of this glass lens,

128
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:56,960
