131
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:03,760
It was you that day,

132
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:04,560
Indeed it was.

133
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:07,120
I did go to the black market auction that day.

134
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,360
This glass lens

135
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:11,160
