136
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:18,000
Are you trying to charge me with theft, sir?

137
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:21,760
This glass lens was originally a treasure of the Situ family.

138
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:25,160
