142
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:31,040
I have some savings from running my teahouse.

143
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,480
The world is in chaos these days.

144
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:34,640
I want to collect rare treasures like the glass lens

145
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:35,760
to preserve their value.

146
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:37,760
As for the Blue Ghost Bandit you mentioned,

147
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:39,090
