148
00:08:40,159 --> 00:08:41,620
I have nothing to explain.

149
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:44,400
Back then, the Blue Ghost Bandit caused havoc in the imperial court,

150
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:46,260
